16#include "api/sequence_checker.h"
17#include "rtc_base/task_utils/to_queued_task.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20
21BalancedConstraint::BalancedConstraint(
22 DegradationPreferenceProvider* degradation_preference_provider)
23 : encoder_target_bitrate_bps_(absl::nullopt),
24 degradation_preference_provider_(degradation_preference_provider) {
25 RTC_DCHECK(degradation_preference_provider_);
26 sequence_checker_.Detach();
27}
28
29void BalancedConstraint::OnEncoderTargetBitrateUpdated(
30 absl::optional<uint32_t> encoder_target_bitrate_bps) {
31 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
32 encoder_target_bitrate_bps_ = std::move(encoder_target_bitrate_bps);
33}
34
35bool BalancedConstraint::IsAdaptationUpAllowed(
36 const VideoStreamInputState& input_state,
37 const VideoSourceRestrictions& restrictions_before,
38 const VideoSourceRestrictions& restrictions_after) const {
39 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
40 // Don't adapt if BalancedDegradationSettings applies and determines this will
41 // exceed bitrate constraints.
42 if (degradation_preference_provider_->degradation_preference() ==
43 DegradationPreference::BALANCED) {
44 if (!balanced_settings_.CanAdaptUp(
45 input_state.video_codec_type(),
46 input_state.frame_size_pixels().value(),
47 encoder_target_bitrate_bps_.value_or(0))) {
48 return false;
49 }
50 if (DidIncreaseResolution(restrictions_before, restrictions_after) &&
51 !balanced_settings_.CanAdaptUpResolution(
52 input_state.video_codec_type(),
53 input_state.frame_size_pixels().value(),
54 encoder_target_bitrate_bps_.value_or(0))) {
55 return false;
56 }
57 }
58 return true;
59}
